{"tid":185647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死4隻]工人墮排污井　同事施救齊中毒釀五死傷","createTime":"2017-04-03T15:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T01:47:04.000Z","uid":32407,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63756cb98afdfecd2bbfd23edb5dfcaabd128020","tid":185647,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170403/bkncn-20170403174012202-0403_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170403%2Fbkncn-20170403174012202-0403_05011_001.html&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7f7c23f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170403/bkncn-20170403174012202-0403_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170403/photo/bkncn-20170403174012202-0403_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170403%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170403174012202-0403_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a74d58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南湘鄉市澳泉食品有限公司今日上午發生一宗窒息中毒事故，造成四死一傷，傷者正在醫院接受治療，相關負責人已被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n據湘鄉市政府消息稱，事發在今日上午約11時35分，澳泉食品有限公司聘請湘潭市潔寶清潔服務有限公司清理化糞池時，一名員工不慎掉落排污井，其他員工發現後嘗試救人，但不幸一同掉落。從網傳短片所見，墮井者被救出時已不省人事。事故共造成四死一傷。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，內地過去不時發生工人在排污井內吸入沼氣中毒的事故。據了解，沼氣的主要成分是甲烷、二氧化碳、氮和少量的硫化氫、氫、一氧化碳等。當沼氣達到一定濃度時，人進入沼氣池，會發生窒息性中毒，嚴重者可致命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bb67aa5cc3fa291b607d9264f3405e5d586dc6","tid":185647,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"無害"},{"pid":"4888c2e87ff5bbb1239239ec8b806b41d8e47518","tid":185647,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"如果咁都令你開心 我真心為你感到悲哀"},{"pid":"a2ff55838cb0a12bacdda7156ad6447dad9bc2fc","tid":185647,"uid":10890,"li